{
  "texts": [
    "The dataset is divided into three parts: a training set (10,875 elements), a test set (7425 elements), and a validation set (3730 elements).",
    "One important point to note is that the CRAFT dataset does not have a Spanish equivalent.",
    "Given the scarcity of datasets in Spanish for the biomedical domain, we would like to offer new ways to improve biomedical systems for Spanish users.",
    "As a result, to boost the dataset's size, we used data augmentation techniques.",
    "Data augmentation is a strategy to increase a system's performance by generating more training data."
  ]
}